headline: Northern Trust Selected as Custodian for $18.5 Billion State of New Mexico Educational Retirement Board Public Fund
summary: CHICAGO, August 26, 2025--Northern Trust will provide services including performance measurement and advanced support for alternative and derivative investments in the fund.
